{"product_id":"hoia-fruit-acid-face-mask-fruitfest-50ml","title":"HOIA Fruit Acid Face Mask Fruitfest 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe mask containing fruit acids (AHA) and natural salicylic acid (BHA) helps to exfoliate dead skin cells, while simultaneously stimulating the production of new skin cells and collagen in the skin. The mask helps moisturize the skin, prevent the formation of pigmentation spots, alleviate acne, smooth out superficial wrinkles, make the skin more elastic and give the complexion a fresh and radiant appearance.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Cleanse the skin of makeup residues and apply a suitable amount to damp skin, avoiding the eye and lip areas, and leave the mask on for 5-10 minutes. Then rinse thoroughly with warm water and apply serum, oil or cream to the skin. Use 1-2 times a week. Discontinue use if rash, itching, or burning occurs during use. Mild tingling on the face is natural.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHowever, it is important to use AHA acids cautiously, especially on sensitive skin, and apply sunscreen to the skin if necessary, as acids can make the skin more sensitive to UV rays.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Rosa Damascena Distillate, *Citrus Aurantium Flower Distillate, Sargassum Fluitans Extract, *Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, *Simmondsia Chinensis oil, Salix Nigra extract, Saccharum Officinarum Extract, Vaccinium Myrtillus Extract, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Extract, Acer Saccharum Extract, Citrus Medica Limonum Extract, Xanthan Gum, Pentylene Glycol, Water, Hibiscus Sabdariffa Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydrolized Sodium Hyaluronate, Lactobacillus Ferment, Kaolin. *Organic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104830095687,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-fruit-acid-face-mask-fruitfest-50ml-877573.jpg?v=1740808668","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hoia-fruit-acid-face-mask-fruitfest-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}